        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2>Timeframe</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap -mx-2">
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 px-2 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <img
              src="https://placehold.co/100x100"
              alt="Phase 1 icon representing evaluation, research, and recommended improvements"
              class="mb-2"
            />
            <h3>Phase 1</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Evaluation, research, and recommended improvements
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 px-2 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <img
              src="https://placehold.co/100x100"
              alt="Phase 2 icon representing estimation of future demand, cost, and including expanded service area"
              class="mb-2"
            />
            <h3>Phase 2</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Estimation of future demand, cost, and including expanded service
              area
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 px-2 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow text-center">
            <img
              src="https://placehold.co/100x100"
              alt="Phase 3 icon representing implementation plan"
              class="mb-2"
            />
            <h3>Phase 3</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Implementation plan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="stakeholders" class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Stakeholder Committee
      </h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
          NFTA-Metro has engaged a Stakeholder Committee to provide feedback and
          insight throughout the course of the study. Committee members include
          (but are not limited to) representatives from:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600">
          <li>Community Services for Every1</li>
          <li>Deaf Access Services</li>
          <li>Erie County</li>
          <li>Independent Living of Niagara County</li>
          <li>Hearts and Hands</li>
          <li>Niagara Frontier Development of the Visually Impaired</li>
          <li>People Inc.</li>
          <li>Progressive County Office of Aging</li>
          <li>WNYIL</li>
          <li>Western New York Independent Living</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="documents" class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2>Project Documents</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col bg-white p-[var(--space-m)] rounded-lg shadow">
        <h3 class="text-s-fluid mb-[var(--space-2xs)]">May 2022 Meeting</h3>
        <ul
          class="font-body text-2xs-fluid list-none space-y-[var(--space-3xs)] mb-[var(--space-l)]"
        >
          <li>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="/assets/pdf/NFTA-Metro-Paratransit-Study-May-22-2023-Stakeholder-Meeting-Presentation-Slides.pdf"
              class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-800"
              >Stakeholder Committee 1 - Meeting Presentation Slides</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="/assets/pdf/NFTA-Metro-Paratransit-Study-External-Stakeholder-Meeting-Summary-May-22-2022.pdf"
              class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700"
              >Stakeholder Committee 1 - Meeting Notes</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="text-s-fluid mb-[var(--space-2xs)]">August 2022 Meeting</h3>
        <ul
          class="font-body text-2xs-fluid list-none space-y-[var(--space-3xs)]"
        >
          <li></li>
          <li>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="/assets/pdf/NFTA-Metro-Paratransit-Study-Draft-Communications-and-Participation-Plan.pdf"
              class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700"
              >Draft Communications & Participation Plan</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="/assets/pdf/Stakeholder-Committee-Meeting-2-Presentation-Slides.pdf"
              class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700"
              >Stakeholder Committee Meeting 2 - Presentation Slides</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="src/assets/pdf/Stakeholder-Committee-Meeting-2-Summary.pdf"
              class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700"
              >Stakeholder Committee Meeting 2 - Meeting Summary</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
        <form
          name="contact"
          action="https://usebasin.com/f/a95a0d1def96"
          method="POST"
          enctype="multipart/form-data"
          id="form"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="name" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2"
              >Your name (required)</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label
              for="email"
              class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2"
              >Your email (required)</label
            >
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label
              for="message"
              class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Message</label
            >
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="4"
              class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <input
            type="submit"
            class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline"
          />
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
